articles.author: David L. Stern, Ellen Francis
articles.title: Europeans rally around Ukraine after Trump insults Zelensky - The Washington Post
articles.description: President Donald Trump’s promotion of Russia’s narrative has caused worry in Europe that the United States is redrawing its long-standing alliances.
